OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with clear spells becoming
OL,7,Fmore prolonged as cloud clears.
OL,8,FRemaining dry overnight with mostly
OL,9,Fclear skies, leading to a cold night
OL,10,Fwith a widespread frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start for many
OL,13,Fit will be a dry day with long spells
OL,14,Fof sunshine.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,17,Fwith outbreaks of rain through Sunday
OL,18,Fand Monday with winds strengthening,
OL,19,Fbut still some good dry and bright or
OL,20,Fsunny spells. A mostly dry day Tuesday
OL,21,Fwith sunny spells.
